    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"People always told me that I wasn't cut for this line of work. That I was too soft.\"</em></p><h5 id=\"prerequisites\">Prerequisites</h5><p>Have levels in the Medic-Nin class.</p><h5 id=\"benefit\">Benefit</h5><p>During a short rest you may use your hit and chakra dice on other players. You half the amount they would gain from your Hit and Chakra dice. You also increase the Rejuveanting Rest from d6 to d8.</p><h5 id=\"negative\">Negative</h5><p>You cannot use the Take Life feature.</p>",
